{"tid":1679149,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"醒醒啦, 香港人! 和理非要進化, 唔好再捐錢去買飯卷, 唔好再捐錢俾星火!","createTime":"2019-10-28T04:39:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T05:58:12.000Z","uid":273350,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0444d93efed530f50b3502faa646ca187e3e5d77","tid":1679149,"uid":273350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T04:39:18.000Z","msg":"Sorry, 用標題引左你入黎. 但坦白講, 你地捐錢可以捐幾耐呀, 捐一年半載? <span style=\"color: red;\">打場官司都幾年, 呢場抗爭打幾十年架喎! 我們係咪要諗長遠d, 點先可以有資金去支持場運動呀? </span><br />\n<br />\n共產黨有水喉射住, 每個月有新資金去打呢場仗, 我地呢? 一盤散沙, 各有各做. 一窩蜂買飯卷, 一窩蜂捐錢去星火, 結果資源錯配. 隔幾個月, 熱情退卻左, 個D 機構無人捐錢, 營運都出現問題, 結果呢場抗爭就gg啦.&nbsp;<span style=\"color: red;\">共產黨有無限資金, 因為佢地每個月都有收入ma, 而我地要每個月拎錢出黎補貼個運動呀! </span><br />\n<br />\n我地要跟Starman 學習, 每個人要有主動收入, 亦都要被動收入. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢場運動亦需要兩個輪推動抗爭, 呢場運動先有力量向前衝, 咁呢場仗先可以長久打落去.&nbsp;</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我諗到既方案如下:&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n每人每個月捐100元, 只要有1萬個香港人捐錢, 每個月就有100萬進帳, 1年就1200萬. 由於錢少, 同減少人手操作的錯誤, 所有錢只會用黎買香港央行 &quot;匯豐&quot;, 年息約5%, 每年就有60萬的利息.&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n每季都會收到利息, 利息的用途會分為3部份:<br />\n<br />\n1. 支援被捕人士 (eg. 捐去星火)<br />\n<br />\n2. 支援青年 (eg. 買飯卷)<br />\n<br />\n3. 協助受害人控告政府濫捕<br />\n<br />\n60萬好似好少, 但我地的本金係未動過, 所以當我地繼續籌款, 第2年亦籌到1200萬時, 基金就會有2400萬, 利息就會有120萬. 換言之, <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">當雪球不斷滾, 香港人的力量會越來越大.&nbsp;</span></span><br />\n<br />\n行動目標：<br />\n0 -&gt;100萬：我會使用早前開設的公司戶口 (無限公司), 進行眾籌集資100萬. 我的公司戶口內的1萬多元會用作眾籌或相關所使用的費用.&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n100萬 -&gt; 1000萬：於HSBC 開設有限公司戶口, 並將所有資金撥進去. 由大家推舉可信的3位連登人 , 然後一齊開戶口. 而戶口提款必須由我 (Tier 1) 和連登人 (Tier 2) 共同簽名作實. 而那3個連登人將就上述3個利息用途設立 telegram group , 並就就各自範疇討論資金應投放那個機構, 並每季以投票方式決定利息捐往那個機構. 當投票完成後, 連登人將利用tier 2 的權限申請轉款, 然後我批核. 換言之, 我的角色只係當大家決定捐去邊, 我就批核將錢捐去邊. 目的是制衡各方權力.&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n1000萬 -&gt; 1億：設立海外戶口, 利用捐款, 將海外香港人和國際力量凝聚. 設立自動轉帳, 方便每個人每個月都能自動捐款. 推出香港人信用卡, 當消費時, 亦能支持抗爭.&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n1億 -&gt; 10億：成立基金會, 所有公司持份者退場, 基金將由所有香港人共同擁有, 由香港人一人一票選出管理團隊, 由團隊決定資金用途.&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">10億打後：之後點走, 由香港人話事</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果大家有此計劃有任何疑問, 請留言問我, 我會盡快解答. 所有資料我都係從網上和個人經驗所想出來, 相信會有缺失. 有冇連登巴打有相同諗法可以交流下, 懇求各位連登朋友對此計劃提出任何建議/ 批評, 我將會參考建議完善呢個計劃. 然後, 於11月尾開始眾籌!&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n光復香港, 時代抗命! <br />\n香港人, 反抗!"},{"pid":"3f4bae498792124efdb2085fb9a9420fa601921e","tid":1679149,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T04:39:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T7kDwBC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT7kDwBC.jpg&h=6da1c92c&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"3d7a8bff8b6c6b6a6b1dc88ef2371410dba21b20","tid":1679149,"uid":273350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T04:42:00.000Z","msg":"自推十連 1/10 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"398804ef899c1ecc2c7c29a1fd19d86f3caf22b1","tid":1679149,"uid":273350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T04:42:48.000Z","msg":"自推十連 2/10 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa30335290b8c1ef3f422dfb21606675c9b3744e","tid":1679149,"uid":273350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T04:43:27.000Z","msg":"自推十連 3/10 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0711c7091c5a9a5c08160c835e6dc2d55cefe209","tid":1679149,"uid":273350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T04:43:50.000Z","msg":"自推十連 4/10 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb740759cf28e2d70e019d384491a4890034f64d","tid":1679149,"uid":273350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T04:44:11.000Z","msg":"自推十連 5/10 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eac398f8be3639476a233dfe86f47718f13821a","tid":1679149,"uid":273350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T04:44:32.000Z","msg":"自推十連 6/10 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a7a15344cd724352305e43146f4304f5cc6089d","tid":1679149,"uid":273350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T04:45:03.000Z","msg":"自推十連 7/10 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ca07fd089e17c7fbdcef50918da21a9c177cfb6","tid":1679149,"uid":273350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T04:45:20.000Z","msg":"自推十連 8/10 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1e9827edecbf59e85c230117992a604d8fe3167","tid":1679149,"uid":273350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T04:45:36.000Z","msg":"自推十連 9/10 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eb17c2f3a7ddee5f360e49248ede570e0ce58fa","tid":1679149,"uid":273350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T04:46:10.000Z","msg":"自推十連 10/10 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b6d698b9f1170e26820d5943628c018acb46632","tid":1679149,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T04:57:57.000Z","msg":"邊個信得過人可以渣果舊錢"},{"pid":"1f9bad5d1f7e306497cad21e629590bc2113646c","tid":1679149,"uid":282115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T05:04:27.000Z","msg":"要有信得過既人揸手咼"},{"pid":"5250b68b9834aa8c7f01bf6515f15d8c9a041af4","tid":1679149,"uid":137727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T05:05:28.000Z","msg":"有得諗但搵邊個搞"},{"pid":"ff288e72065e146b0ea1d20fe1df40807dc79865","tid":1679149,"uid":305009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T05:08:28.000Z","msg":"樓豬P牌<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢個唔係問題<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最怕樓豬同啲甩P五毛一撚樣"},{"pid":"14a5376c0537c766c4992dc07503a6924ca44d26","tid":1679149,"uid":273350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T05:11:56.000Z","msg":"人係有貪念, 當筆錢越大, 我都信唔過我自己.<br />\n<br />\n所以, 用我個人公司入款的時候, 我會交出我所有權限, 同埋取消網上轉帳. 咁個戶口就只有入, 無法出數. 同時會加連登仔為通知人, 如果有人係戶口提款, 連登仔會立即知道.<br />\n<br />\n到開左有限公司, 每筆數出都要2個人審批. 由負責項目的連登仔申請轉帳, 而我只係確認轉帳.<br />\n<br />\n最理想就係個戶口自動運作, 有錢就買匯豐, 收到利息就捐出黎. <br />\n<br />\n大家覺得仲有咩方法可以減少個人對戶口的操控? 請大家俾d 意見 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa7ac38138d69420dfb12986784fdd667f5d46cf","tid":1679149,"uid":273350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff288e72065e146b0ea1d20fe1df40807dc79865","tid":1679149,"uid":305009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T05:08:28.000Z","msg":"樓豬P牌<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢個唔係問題<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最怕樓豬同啲甩P五毛一撚樣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T05:34:38.000Z","msg":"我以前唔上連登. 我以前唔理政治, 打份牛工, 但識得少少投資, 所以生活都尚好. <br />\n<br />\n係因為呢場運動, 令我知道香港人要行動. 所以, 我用返以前hku 個email 開連登戶口, 所以我一直都係 P 牌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢段期間, 我和其他有心人一樣, 聯系左我身邊的一班相同理念的朋友, 大家一齊捐錢去幫班靚仔. 因為呢個契機, 我重用返以前的公司戶口去管理資金.<br />\n<br />\n呢段日子大家都不斷進步, 我覺得呢個捐款戶口應該都要進化. 我們要用時間幫資金增值, 咁先可以提高香港人嬴的機會.<br />\n<br />\n我亦不斷進步, 希望有一日成為真正的連登人啦! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc797e8181fc08a871a0d384c4ea04984c704101","tid":1679149,"uid":273350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5250b68b9834aa8c7f01bf6515f15d8c9a041af4","tid":1679149,"uid":137727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T05:05:28.000Z","msg":"有得諗但搵邊個搞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T05:42:29.000Z","msg":"一人計短, 二人計長/ 大家一齊傾點樣搞, 我可以將我之前同朋友夾的萬幾元捐出黎, 做成立呢個基金的行政費."},{"pid":"561f24653e9afa32c9e836402c551bbc4f86b19d","tid":1679149,"uid":273350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f9bad5d1f7e306497cad21e629590bc2113646c","tid":1679149,"uid":282115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T05:04:27.000Z","msg":"要有信得過既人揸手咼"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T05:58:12.000Z","msg":"人係信唔過, 你睇下警察有左權力後, 腐敗得幾快就知.<br />\n<br />\n所以, 我地要設立個制度去管理筆錢, 設計到筆錢係要經過程序去批, 而不是某個人決定, 將人治的元素減到最低."}]}